<div id="descriptionContainer">
  
      <div id="description" class="readable stacked" style="right:0">
        
<span id="freeTextContainer15493809047758553881">Like <i>Brick Lane</i> and <i>The Kite Runner</i>, Camilla Gibb&apos;s widely praised new novel is a poignant and intensely atmospheric look beyond the stereotypes of Islam. After her hippie British parents are murdered, Lilly is raised at a Sufi shrine in Morocco. As a young woman she goes on pilgrimage to Harar, Ethiopia, where she teaches Qur&apos;an to children and falls in love with an ideal</span>
  <span id="freeText15493809047758553881" style="display:none">Like <i>Brick Lane</i> and <i>The Kite Runner</i>, Camilla Gibb's widely praised new novel is a poignant and intensely atmospheric look beyond the stereotypes of Islam. After her hippie British parents are murdered, Lilly is raised at a Sufi shrine in Morocco. As a young woman she goes on pilgrimage to Harar, Ethiopia, where she teaches Qur'an to children and falls in love with an idealistic doctor. But even swathed in a traditional headscarf, Lilly can't escape being marked as a foreigner. Forced to flee Ethiopia for England, she must once again confront the riddle of who she is and where she belongs.</span>
  <a data-text-id="15493809047758553881" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

