<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/16568448-brianna-daub"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/f_100x100-6433b08cbe793211f55e184d39e84c4d.png" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/16568448-brianna-daub">Brianna Daub</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">It was that she had stayed in his palace on his hospitality, and that this was supposedly because her guardian was a friend of his. It is also mention<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">It was that she had stayed in his palace on his hospitality, and that this was supposedly because her guardian was a friend of his. It is also mentioned a couple of times that Selassie 'loved' foreigners/Westerners, so that may have also played a role.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
